 original-img="https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250514/20250514_a722ec3f72ba4c3a6e57GBBidAB2EspK.png"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/5ecfd7/f/800x0/https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250514/20250514_a722ec3f72ba4c3a6e57GBBidAB2EspK.png"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="t_attach" id="attach_16222929_menu" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img alt="" border="0" class="absmiddle" src="images/attachicons/image.gif"/&gt; &lt;a href="attachment.php?aid=16222929&amp;amp;nothumb=yes" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Screenshot_20250512-095918.png&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt; (1.62 MB)&lt;br/&gt;&lt;div class="t_smallfont"&gt;2025-5-14 07:07&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31926819&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=170729299168245943e4b689_25895394"/><published>2025-05-14T07:07:27+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>e645d088048267bfa18ddaab1db653bd</id><title>港匯又退返去弱方保証,有冇傻仔上左當？</title><updated>2025-05-14T09:05:29+08:00</updated><author><name>CC_CHAN256</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-05-14T09:05:29+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_572395287"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_572395287"&gt;港匯又退去返弱方保証,有冇傻仔上左當被呃上車？&lt;span id="attach_16223053" onmouseover="showMenu(this.id, 0, 1)" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="images/discuss_style/attachimg.gif"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div class="post-img-container" data-pid="572395287" original-img="https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250514/20250514_33ce2e717d3658bb35a0CVJ5dyxII7iy.jpg"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/b7b5d3/f/800x0/https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250514/20250514_33ce2e717d3658bb35a0CVJ5dyxII7iy.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="t_attach" id="attach_16223053_menu" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img alt="" border="0" class="absmiddle" src="images/attachicons/image.gif"&gt; &lt;a href="attachment.php?aid=16223053&amp;amp;nothumb=yes" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Screenshot_2025-05-14-09-03-13-630_com.mi.globalbrowser.jpg&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt; (381.96 KB)&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="t_smallfont"&gt;2025-5-14 09:05&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;[&lt;span style="font-style: italic;"&gt; 本帖最後由 CC_CHAN256 於 2025-5-14 16:46 編輯 &lt;/span&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31926926&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=170729299168245943e4b689_25895394"/><published>2025-05-14T09:05:29+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>201941b53ac593f3d1f03573d686e3e1</id><title>請教 - 深井 青龍頭 汀九 荃西一帶 會唔會好吵 好大飛機噪音？？</title><updated>2025-05-14T09:27:30+08:00</updated><author><name>macrohard</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-05-14T09:27:30+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_572395513"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_572395513"&gt;如標題所述&lt;br&gt;深井 青龍頭 汀九 荃西一帶 會唔會好吵 好大飛機噪音？？&lt;br/&gt;分幾鐘就有一架飛機起落，係頭頂飛過。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;請教，&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;有住開果頭架 c hing 分享下感受&lt;/span&gt;，有冇得避。&lt;br/&gt;.&lt;br/&gt;&lt;img alt="" border="0" smilieid="190" src="https://www.discuss.com.hk/images/smilies/chingcze/chingcze_16.gif"/&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31926942&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=170729299168245943e4b689_25895394"/><published>2025-05-14T09:27:30+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>c8cfc3c40aca72de00021af6526013d9</id><title>烏溪沙星漣海三房855萬沽創同戶型新低 原業主持貨四年賬面蝕325萬元</title><updated>2025-05-14T09:36:49+08:00</updated><author><name>onnam</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-05-14T09:36:49+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_572395612"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_572395612"&gt;該行最新一宗烏溪沙星漣海三房單位成交，獲同區客以855萬元承接，成交價創該屋苑三房戶型新低，首次跌穿860萬元水平。&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;李天傑表示，成交單位為烏溪沙星漣海3B座低層E室，實用面積769方呎，採三房設計，向東享海景。據了解，單位最初叫價899萬元，獲同區客垂青。買家考慮到物業樓齡僅約七年，屬區內較新住宅項目，加上單位坐擁海景優勢，內櫳裝修企理，業主最終願意議價，雙方以855萬元達成交易，實用呎價約11,118元。成交價創該屋苑三房戶型新低，首次跌穿860萬元水平。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;資料顯示，原業主於2021年1,180萬元購入單位，持貨約四年，賬面蝕約325萬元，蝕幅約27.5%。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;西沙震散烏溪沙二手。&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31926949&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=170729299168245943e4b689_25895394"/><published>2025-05-14T09:36:49+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>0be660f64fa8db8f5c657b758f99092d</id><title>恒生銀行裁員5成人。給裁員員工可否向恆生申請免供樓一年嗎。如果年輕員工再買樓大負資產下。唉</title><updated>2025-05-14T11:48:21+08:00</updated><author><name>edwin8888</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-05-14T11:48:21+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_572397296"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_572397296"&gt;&lt;span id="attach_16223282" onmouseover="showMenu(this.id, 0, 1)" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="images/discuss_style/attachimg.gif"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div class="post-img-container" data-pid="572397296" original-img="https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250514/20250514_c5841386